A simple getWork pool for ethereum mining

Payouts are still manual. TODO: write payouts when someone mines 10 blocks. Also, make the submit actually check the return code

Use with ethminer to mine cheapETH

# while true; do ./ethminer -P http://pool.cheapeth.org:8080/<your address>; sleep 1; done

Use CUDA instead, instead of OpenCL.

# while true; do ./ethminer -P http://pool.cheapeth.org:8080/<your address> --cuda; sleep 1; done

Learn more about cheapeth at https://cheapeth.org

